---
title: Quick Creamy Beef & Leek Spaghetti with Balsamic Salad & Herbs
description: Here’s a new delectable combination for pasta night. We’ve paired seasoned beef with cooked leek and a side of fresh salad to
ensure your mouth-waters as they all come together in the bowl. And of course, add Parmesan cheese!

